{"tid":1754721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"贏咗區選 之後行動要向咩方向發展","createTime":"2019-11-25T10:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T11:32:35.000Z","uid":244387,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"169fedd8b9114871d06b291bdf64f60bc1d8079c","tid":1754721,"uid":244387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:00:19.000Z","msg":"黎明行動依家好似冇咗嗰種感覺 <br />\n大遊行又九成都唔撚批 <br />\n除咗12.8嘅集會嚟緊好似冇乜較大型行動 <br />\n嚟緊條路可以點行<br />\n我真係諗唔到<br />\n亦都唔知可以點 <br />\n區選贏咗 <br />\n但係我哋仲係輸緊好多嘢<br />\n我哋唔可以停 <br />\n唔可以就咁完咗場運動 <br />\n我哋仲有好多嘢未攞返 <br />\n希望大家可以喺度討論下嚟緊要點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc099af455390d596dfa5886a354bade7c01207","tid":1754721,"uid":244387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:00:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"933c293543ad781867f787d6e6929c3d53e39d8c","tid":1754721,"uid":244387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:01:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3231e136a5221b868f8de68bb3c1806dfa68d37d","tid":1754721,"uid":244387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:01:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b065bde1ccc7231c81f5815124dfe0ab8c9bc60","tid":1754721,"uid":244387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:03:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20270efc7e2e143242f7913762419e40b9917346","tid":1754721,"uid":244387,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:04:31.000Z","msg":"之後可以點 係咪會繼續黎明行動？"},{"pid":"e82fd8481041d686c8963e4769fccda93a285d7b","tid":1754721,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:05:16.000Z","msg":"屆屈都選舉不公<br />\n麻煩搞搞佢啦<br />\n邊有可能主觀判斷廢票當有效票<br />\n掌心雷<br />\n一車車旅遊巴<br />\n又派枕頭<br />\n身份證被盗用 被投票<br />\n做實事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2659d327c94862f5b74b0169431fdc5812d334","tid":1754721,"uid":244387,"like":